<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>1259</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 shén a nǐ réng shì wǒ men de fù nǐ shì yáo jiàng wǒ men shì ní tǔ
 qiú nǐ bù yào fā nù bù yào jì niàn wǒ men de zuì qiú nǐ cóng gāo tiān chuí gù
 nǐ de shèng yì biàn wèi kuàng yě yé lù sā lěng biàn wèi huāng chǎng
 shèng jié huá měi de diàn bèi huǒ fén shāo suǒ xiàn mù de měi de jǐn dōu huāng fèi
 shén a shén a yǒu zhè xiē shì nǐ hái rěn dé zhù ma
 nǐ réng jìng mò shǐ wǒ men kū qì ma wǒ men shēn xìn nǐ bì lái zhěng jiù</lyrics>
<title>shén a nǐ réng shì wǒ men de fù 迦南1259</title>
</song>